										<content:encoded><![CDATA[<p><a href="https://www.binance.com/en-NG/activity/referral/offers" data-wpel-link="external" rel="external noopener noreferrer"><span style="font-weight: 400;">The Binance Referral Program</span></a><span style="font-weight: 400;"> is designed to reward both new and existing users. It gives current Binance members an incentive to invite their friends to the platform, while new users enjoy a welcome bonus when they register with a Binance referral code. In 2026, the active Binance referral code <strong>VB2025</strong> provides up to 100 USD in signup rewards, making it one of the most attractive offers for beginners.</span></p>
<p>Inside this guide, you will find both the necessary referral codes and the exact instructions for redeeming your signup bonus.</p>
<h2><span style="font-weight: 400;">What is Binance Referral Code?</span></h2>
