<p class="font-claude-response-body break-words whitespace-normal">The Binance invite code is used during the registration process to establish a connection between the new user&#8217;s account and the referrer. By utilizing this code, you activate special promotional bonuses and simultaneously ensure that the inviting party receives their corresponding benefits.</p>
<p>New users usually benefit through incentives like reduced trading fees, cashback rewards, or by redeeming a valid binance voucher code. These incentives are often part of a larger binance promo campaign. As an example, applying a working <b data-path-to-node="17,0" data-index-in-node="238">binance voucher code 2026</b> like VB2025 can give new members the chance to receive up to $100 back in trading fees once they meet the deposit requirement.</p>
