</table>
<p>The inviter&#8217;s benefits are determined by the specific referral mode. One option is a single bonus, identical to the one the invitee gets for using the Binance referral code. Another option provides the inviter with a continuous commission, earning them a percentage of the new account&#8217;s trading fees.</p>
<h3><b>Types of Binance Referral Code</b></h3>
<p><span style="font-weight: 400;">Binance splits its referral program into two options.</span></p>
<p><b>Referral Mode (Lite Referral):</b><span style="font-weight: 400;"> This one’s simple. A new user signs up with your code, finishes KYC, and drops in at least $50 within two weeks. Both of you get a $100 trading fee voucher. Quick, one-time bonus. Good for beginners who just want something right away.</span></p>
<p><b>Referral Pro (Standard Referral):</b><span style="font-weight: 400;"> This is the long game. Instead of a single voucher, you keep earning a cut of the trading fees whenever that person trades on Spot, Margin, or Futures. As long as they keep trading, you keep collecting.</span></p>
<h2><span style="font-weight: 400;">Binance Sign-Up Bonus for Referral Code <strong>vb2025</strong></span></h2>
<p><span style="font-weight: 400;">By using the Binance referral code </span><strong>V</strong><span style="font-weight: 400;"><strong>B2025</strong> during registration, new users unlock a special reward package. The main attraction here is a $100 signup bonus, which Binance applies in the form of a trading fee rebate voucher.</span></p>
<p><b>Bonus Rewards</b><b><br />
</b><span style="font-weight: 400;">The way it works is simple. Create your account, complete identity verification (KYC), and then deposit at least $50 within the first two weeks. Once that’s done, the bonus voucher shows up in your account automatically. The binance sign up bonus 2026 is tied directly to this step, making it basically a binance first deposit bonus since no deposit means no reward.</span></p>
